highlights.text: EsDeeKid has the most spots on Viral Songs Finland. “Phantom” is the highest at #32.
“Jos tänään tuntuu pahalta” by HAGES is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Finland at #2.
“Mun ihminen” by ELLIMEI has been on Viral Songs Finland the longest, at 155 days straight.
“Bones” by Amorphis is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Finland, up 12 spots at #52.
